==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌmp|-ʌmp]]

===Noun===
'''thump'''
# a [[blow]] that produces a [[muffled]] [[sound]]
# the sound of such a blow; a [[thud]]
===Verb===
'''to thump'''  (''transitive'')
# to [[hit]] someone so as to make such a sound
'''to thump'''  (''intransitive'')
# to [[thud]] or [[pound]]
# to [[throb]] with a muffled [[rhythmic]] sound